p to 25,600 and zero smoothing or acceleration.\", \"13 programmable buttons including a repositionable DPI-shift (sniper) button.\", \"LIGHTSYNC RGB flows beautifully across 8 customizable zones.\", \"Comfort-focused ergonomics with textured thumb rest and durable build.\", \"USB-C fast charging delivers hours of play in minutes.\", \"Compatible with Logitech PowerPlay wireless charging (sold separately).\", \"Ideal for FPS, MOBA, RTS, and productivity with full onboard profile storage and macros.\"]',71),(65,12999,4.9,88,'In Stock','Razer India','2–5 business days via Bluedart or Delhivery','{\"DPI\": \"Up to 30,000\", \"Sensor\": \"Razer Focus Pro 30K Optical\", \"Weight\": \"63g\", \"Switches\": \"Optical Gen-3\", \"Battery Life\": \"Up to 90 hours (via 2.4GHz)\"}','[\"The Razer DeathAdder V3 Pro is the ultimate evolution of one of the most iconic gaming mice, made lighter and faster for esports dominance.\", \"Only 63g — extremely lightweight while keeping Razer’s legendary ergonomic shape.\", \"Powered by the Razer Focus Pro 30K optical sensor for flawless tracking and precision.\", \"2.4GHz Razer HyperSpeed Wireless ensures ultra-low latency for pro-level performance.\", \"Third-gen Razer Optical Mouse Switches offer lightning-fast response with zero double-click issues.\", \"Customizable DPI stages and lift-off distance for enhanced control.\", \"Textured side grip and smooth matte surface for stable handling.\", \"Compatible with Razer HyperPolling Wireless Dongle (sold separately) for 4000Hz polling.\", \"USB-C charging port with included Speedflex cable — use wired or wireless.\", \"Ideal for competitive FPS, MOBA, and battle royale players demanding every edge.\"]',72),(66,8999,4.7,77,'In Stock','Roccat India','2–5 business days via Bluedart or Delhivery','{\"Sensor\": \"Roccat Owl-Eye 19K (based on PixArt PAW3370)\", \"Weight\": \"75g\", \"Switches\": \"Titan Optical\", \"Connection\": \"2.4GHz Wireless + Bluetooth + USB-C Wired\", \"Battery Life\": \"U